repository-code: "https://github.com/SDerrode/exactIMM"
abstract: >-
  Reference implementation of the AB-constrained Gaussian Switching
  System (GSS) framework: a fast constant-gain exact optimal filter under
  the AB structural assumption, with support for a known exogenous
  input (deterministic command), supervised and semi-supervised parameter
  estimation (Baum-Welch EM), and Monte-Carlo benchmarks including
  real-data studies (vehicle dynamics and NOAA ENSO indices).
keywords:
  - state-space model
  - Markov-switching
  - regime-switching
  - Kalman filter
  - IMM
  - Baum-Welch
  - EM algorithm
  - ENSO
  - signal processing
